flowchart TD
    Start([Start]) --> Login[Candidate authenticates with MFA]
    Login --> Verify{Identity verified?}
    Verify -- No --> Deny[Deny entry and alert recruiter] --> End([End])
    Verify -- Yes --> Begin[Begin assessment]
    Begin --> Fork{{Continuous monitoring}}
    Fork --> F1[Face / identity check]
    Fork --> F2[Phone / object detection]
    Fork --> F3[Gaze & head-pose tracking]
    Fork --> F4[Browser-activity monitoring]
    F1 --> Join{{Aggregate integrity events}}
    F2 --> Join
    F3 --> Join
    F4 --> Join
    Join --> Score[Update weighted risk score]
    Score --> Check{Risk >= threshold?}
    Check -- Yes --> Alert[Raise proportionate alert<br/>in-app / email / SMS]
    Check -- No --> Continue[Continue assessment]
    Alert --> Continue
    Continue --> Done{Assessment submitted?}
    Done -- No --> Fork
    Done -- Yes --> Final[Compute final risk score<br/>and generate report]
    Final --> End
